  "Description": {
    "English": "Though its surface is dirtied and dull, polishing this rock reveals a deep inner glow, a glitter beneath a subtly iridescent surface.<br><br>Select in the Inventory (<span class=\"name name-img\">INVENTORY</span>) and crack open with <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "尽管其表面肮脏而暗淡，这块岩石在抛光后会显现出深层的内在光芒，那是一种细微虹彩表面下的闪光。<br><br>在库存（<span class=\"name name-img\">INVENTORY</span>）中选择它，通过<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>将其砸开。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "雖然表面骯髒暗沉，將岩石拋光後能看到深層的內部光澤，輕微虹光的表面下閃耀著光彩。<br><br>在道具欄（<span class=\"name name-img\">INVENTORY</span>）中選取，再用 <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span> 敲開。"
  },
